{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/game-description-image1.png?t=1734987943\" />Souper Game is a fun and spicy clicker where you play as... SOUP! That's right\u2014an irresistible, hot, and aromatic soup that the elven girl Sylvie prepares for the rude and insatiable Troll. Your mission? Not only to become the perfect dish but also to earn her affection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/steam_text_1.png?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/GIF2.gif?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/steam_text_2.png?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/GIF3.gif?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/steam_text_3.png?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/GIF1.gif?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you whip up the ideal soup, stand your ground against the Troll, and avoid becoming his lunch? Welcome to the world where even soup can be a passionate hero! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/game-description-image2.png?t=1734987943\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0Secret, magical, and rare ingredients that pack a punch with unexpected effects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0A colorful cast of enemies, each with their own unique attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0Fearsome bosses with mechanics that will keep you on your toes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0Three branching storylines shaped by how you upgrade your soup. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0Spicy interactions with Sylvie. How spicy? That\u2019s a secret... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/heart.png?t=1734987943\" />\u00a0Dive into an interactive world\u2014explore, click, and uncover delightful surprises! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/extras/game-description-image3.png?t=1734987943\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734987943","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734987943","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181790/65c87775635e9cd81b312cb5176c40aac339f0c7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=